title: Maruti Suzuki hits milestone with 5,000th service touchpoint opening
description: Maruti Suzuki aims to expand service network following sales increase, reaching 5,000 service touchpoints in India. Hisashi Takeuchi inaugurated the 5000th touchpoint in Gurugram.
